I, Name of Employer Representative, of legal age, with office address at Employer Address after having been sworn to in accordance with law do hereby depose and stated:
I undertake to follow the following requirements hereunder mentioned to wit;
Airfare of the workers shall be shouldered by the employer from point of origin to the place of work and upon completion of contract;
All documentary requirements shall be provided free of charge by the employer including fees related to visa or work permit;
No deductions shall be made from the regular salary of the worker other than the compulsory contributions prescribed by law.
Shall assume joint and solidary liability with the Philippine Recruitment Agency for all claims and liabilities which may arise in connection with the employment of workers, including but not limited to payment of wages, death and disability compensation and repatriation;
Shall guarantee compliance with its contractual obligations as approved by MWO and processed by the DMW;
Shall provide for the best terms and conditions of employment;
Shall repatriate its hired and deployed workers and personal belongings when the need arises; and
Shall assist and cooperate with the MWO, DMW and their Philippine Recruitment Agency on all matters affecting their hired and deployed worker/s.
I am executing this affidavit in compliance with the requirements for the issuance of DMW Registration pursuant to the said rules.
That I am executing this affidavit to attest to the truth of the foregoing facts and comply with whatever legal requirements it may serve.

