Recalling its Resolution ACHPR/ 69(XXXV) 04 of 4 June 2004 on the protection of human rights defenders in Africa, adopted at its 35th Ordinary Session, held from 21 May to 4 June 2004, in Banjul, The Gambia;
Bearing in mind its Resolution 83(XXXVIII) 05 of 5 December 2005 on the Appointment of the Special Rapporteur on Human Rights Defenders in Africa, adopted at the 38th Ordinary Session, held from 21 November to 5 December 2005, in Banjul, The Gambia;
